About the pages
Homepage (UI Design progress 60%)
Main and default page of the website. There's a banner with a background image with a headline text and a button 'Co jsme zač?' (redirecting to About Us page). Underneath is situated a widget with News from the community. It takes posts from Events page and posts manually added from the dashboard. Under this widget are located our social media links. Footer follows.

